nodes.text: G. Bresch was an individual who served as a lieutenant in the Cularin Militia, during the time of the Clone Wars.

Following the publishing of a story on the Cularin holonet node about the Thaereian military officer Nightwing, many people believed that Nightwing may have been Osten Dal'Nay, the commander of the Cularin Militia. A discussion thread was set up on the holonet node to discuss Nightwing and Bresch was tasked with monitoring any postings on the subject of the story.
